><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-1784220595078074&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=2831318673&amp;adf=132027367&amp;pi=t.aa~a.2302158543~i.36~rp.1&amp;w=795&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1683258599&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=2479079003&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=795x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdocsach24.co%2Fdoc-sach%2Fma-long-phien-thien%2Fchuong-2-thien-tai-cung-duong-ha-529081.html&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=199&amp;rw=795&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;adsid=ChEI8K_NogYQ14GEt9_PsZrNARI9AHqKWakBdXe4HqgeuJ-1NNdRXXpSS-YoJ9i8tSWFeO9b0t9FyMSSLnKcxdwBtzPaH3vQT8NO0m0YG3ZvNQ&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiOTguMC40NzU5LjIyIixbXSwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjExMi4wLjU2MTUuMTY1Il0sWyJOb3RfQSBCcmFuZCIsIjI0LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJPcGVyYSBHWCIsIjk4LjAuNDc1OS4yMiJdXSwwXQ..&amp;dt=1683258599517&amp;bpp=4&amp;bdt=772&amp;idt=4&amp;shv=r20230502&amp;mjsv=m202305030101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D624cd4d3ae370e66-223fcd8190e000f2%3AT%3D1683257852%3ART%3D1683257852%3AS%3DALNI_MbLJv_wEG_T9rzzYfvAuxOdGX4HRQ&amp;gpic=UID%3D00000be861d88c74%3AT%3D1683257852%3ART%3D1683257852%3AS%3DALNI_MYnvY_g6fwHty5hWteMuS90toMlkw&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C795x280%2C795x280%2C795x280&amp;nras=5&amp;correlator=4755467155570&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;ga_vid=1620062547.1683257852&amp;ga_sid=1683258599&amp;ga_hid=818944282&amp;ga_fc=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=14&amp;u_h=864&amp;u_w=1536&amp;u_ah=832&amp;u_aw=1536&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1.25&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=343&amp;ady=2293&amp;biw=1481&amp;bih=731&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=44759927%2C44759876%2C44773810%2C42532185%2C42532089%2C44759842%2C31074330%2C44785294%2C44788442%2C44789779&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3671353557628996&amp;tmod=1583847836&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fdocsach24.co%2Fdoc-sach%2Fma-long-phien-thien%2Fchuong-1-thien-tai-cung-duong-thuong-529080.html&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1536%2C0%2C1536%2C832%2C1495%2C731&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;jar=2023-05-05-03&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;xpc=XgPS4LguIN&amp;p=https%3A//docsach24.co&amp;dtd=85\" name=\"aswift_4\" width=\"795\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" data-google-query-id=\"CO3Wlfei3f4CFQYljwodTWAIig\" data-load-complete=\"true\"></iframe></div>\r\n</ins></div>\r\n<p><br><br>Nhưng lúc này, mắt Phong Liệt chợt lóe, lại lần nữa tỉnh táo.<br><br>Nhưng hắn bỗng nổi lên thù hận ngập trời, đột nhiên giận dữ.<br><br>Hắn nghiến răng gầm lên:<br><br><br>- Thì- Ra- Là- Ngươi! Điệp và Long Vũ bị cầm thú nhà ngươi hại chết!<br><br>Long Vũ là một trong bạn tốt tâm giao hiếm hoi của Phong Liệt ở Ma Long giáo, điệp là người hắn thích, hai người này bỗng nhiên tự sát vào mấy năm trước, hiển nhiên tinh thần bị ai khống chế. Bây giờ hắn nghĩ lại, có mười phần toàn do Sở Huyền làm, nỗi hận trong lòng hắn đủ cắn trời nuốt đất.</p>\r\n<div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\"><ins class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1784220595078074\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\">\r\n<div id=\"aswift_5_host\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\"><iframe id=\"aswift_5\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-1784220595078074&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=2831318673&amp;adf=1944505542&amp;pi=t.aa~a.2302158543~i.52~rp.1&amp;w=795&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1683258600&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=2479079003&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=795x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdocsach24.co%2Fdoc-sach%2Fma-long-phien-thien%2Fchuong-2-thien-tai-cung-duong-ha-529081.html&am